            "name": "Season 5",
            "overview": "Premier Danmark, 1/11-2021 På TV2 Charlie  Premier Sverige. 20/2-2023 på CMore klockan 00:01\n\nNew season: 'Sygeplejeskolen' gets a season 5  Nursing school season 4 Photo: Mike Kollöffel / TV 2  By TRINE JERICHAU ROSLEV  1 November 2021  The popular TV 2 series will have a new season in the coming year.  The fourth season of Sygeplejeskolen only just reached its end before TV 2 announced that the series will get another season:  New season about Anna and Ole  Mette Heiberg does not want to reveal much about the upcoming season, but if you follow Anna and Ole's relationship, there seems to be good news:  \"(...)we must see, among other things, whether Anna and Ole's relationship can handle the challenges, now that Ole has been employed in Anna's father's company, and whether Nina and Bent will become a real 50s nuclear family with father, mother and child,\"  says Heiberg about the fifth season.",
